en.title: Meet Our Team
en.description: Bepahkupi's team is a special force. All of whom have different expertise. This is our strength, to create products that can be enjoyed by everyone.

cn.title: 认识我们的团队
cn.description: Bepahkupi的团队是一支特种部队。他们都有不同的专业知识。这是我们的力量，创造了每个人都可以享受的产品。

id.title: Temui Tim Kami
